INSERT OR IGNORE INTO emails (id, doc_id, sender, subject, to_recipients, sent_at, countries, release_batch, epstein_is_sender, is_promotional, all_participants, body)
  VALUES ('vol00009-efta00839629-pdf', 'vol00009-efta00839629-pdf', NULL, 'Question: Start-up in Nigeria, financial projections.', '["jeevacation@gmail.com"]', '2018-04-10T22:53:57.000Z', 'Nigeria, Africa', 9, 0, 0, '  ["jeevacation@gmail.com"] [] [] ', 'Dear Jeffrey,

I hope that this email finds you well and that you had a good Passover celebration.

I wanted to very, very kindly follow up on my previous emails concerning my start-up in Nigeria. I have attached our financial projections and a brief presentation. I am currently seeking USD560K in seed investment (in exchange for equity). I will work (very hard) to try to close a round before I move to Lagos in July.

Recruitment challenges in Africa — most of them stemming from problems in educational systems — are many. The opportunities to capitalize on these challenges are many. Our revenue model draws on Andela and Code Academy''s revenue logics.

I spoke at the Harvard Africa Development Conference a couple of weeks ago — I received very, very positive feedback. The more I speak with organizations, student, and incubators in Nigeria and across Africa, the more convinced I become that amble opportunities to both be profitable yet do social good exist. I have several individuals (with different background and ages) wanting to help me in my work, but in exchange for ''sweat equity'' (which I have neglected).

Ihave afew questions, and I would greatly, greatly value your advice. I would be more than happy to see you at a point andplace the most convenient to you.

I wish you a good afternoon,
Yours sincerely,');

